.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/manual-testing-playbook/ux-hooks/C--comment-hygiene-opencode-plugin.md:3:description: "This scenario validates comment hygiene enforcement for OpenCode sessions in `119-C`. OpenCode has no write-time hook (ADR-001). Enforcement relies on the comment hygiene rule injected via the spec-kit skill-advisor plugin at session start, backed by the git pre-commit gate as the blocking backstop."
