.opencode/skills/cli-external-orchestration/cli-codex/references/cli-reference.md:98:| `--model` | `-m` | `gpt-5.5` | Model to use — `gpt-5.5` (default), `gpt-5.6-luna`, `gpt-5.6-terra`, `gpt-5.6-sol` |
.opencode/skills/cli-external-orchestration/cli-codex/references/cli-reference.md:188:| **GPT-5.6 LUNA** | `gpt-5.6-luna` | `max` | Implementation-heavy work; the `luna-impl` profile pins `max` |
.opencode/skills/cli-external-orchestration/cli-codex/references/cli-reference.md:189:| **GPT-5.6 TERRA** | `gpt-5.6-terra` | `max` | GPT-5.6 fast sibling; no dedicated profile — call directly via `-m gpt-5.6-terra` |
.opencode/skills/cli-external-orchestration/cli-codex/references/cli-reference.md:190:| **GPT-5.6 SOL** | `gpt-5.6-sol` | `ultra` | Verification / review and hardest planning; only model reaching `ultra` (the `sol-verify` profile pins `xhigh`) |
