.opencode/specs/system-code-graph/035-rust-backend-rewrite/001-research/spec.md:64:This is the **ingestion and storage research gate** for packet 011. It defines a future pre-planned **16-round** deep-research pass (single lineage, GPT-5.6-sol at `xhigh` reasoning, `fast` service tier, via the `cli-codex` executor through `/deep:research`) over one bounded body of evidence: source discovery, parser initialization and AST walking, AST-to-node/edge extraction, cross-file edge construction, SQLite graph persistence, edge lifecycle and bitemporal generations, incremental invalidation, and the `code_graph_scan` / `detect_changes` write-index boundary.
