.opencode/skills/sk-design/styles/nornorm/nornorm-canonical.json:237:        "description": "Full-viewport image (leather furniture close-up) with no separate overlay color — the image's own dark tones carry the text contrast. Centered headline in Lunar 48–64px weight 400, color #ffffff, max-width ~800px. Body subtext at 20px weight 400 #ffffff. CTA pair centered below: Primary CTA on the left, Ghost Button on the right, 16px gap."
.opencode/skills/sk-design/styles/nornorm/nornorm-canonical.json:247:        "description": "Vertical stack on a white background: square or 4:3 image at top (no border-radius — images stay sharp-edged), Lunar 20px weight 700 numbered label '01.' in #000000, heading at 20px weight 500 #000000, body copy at 16px weight 400 #6a6a6a Stone. No card chrome, no shadow, no border — the image is the visual frame."
.opencode/skills/sk-design/styles/nornorm/nornorm-canonical.json:252:        "description": "Centered alignment, Lunar 48px weight 400 heading #000000, optional subheading at 20px weight 400 #6a6a6a Stone directly below, 64px bottom margin to the content. No decorative element — the whitespace and centered type are the entire header."
.opencode/skills/sk-design/styles/nornorm/nornorm-canonical.json:274:        "family": "Lunar",
.opencode/skills/sk-design/styles/nornorm/nornorm-canonical.json:281:    "description": "Nornorm's visual system is a near-monochromatic Scandinavian showroom: a white canvas warmed by a bone surface, a single deep cobalt as the only chromatic voice, and a custom geometric typeface (Lunar) tracked tight at -0.03em across every size. The discipline is rationed color — the cobalt appears only on the logo, the primary CTA, and the active state, everything else lives in grayscale. Photography carries the brand's emotional weight: full-bleed editorial interiors, warm leather textures, sculptural paper-craft vignettes, and living office scenes do the storytelling so the interface can stay quiet. Components are flat, pill-shaped, and borderless — a cobalt-filled button next to a dark ghost button, no shadows, no gradients, no decoration beyond generous whitespace and a single accent.",
.opencode/skills/sk-design/styles/nornorm/nornorm-canonical.json:285:        "content": "{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@graph\":[{\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"@id\":\"https://styles.refero.design/style/0769ff4c-f719-4865-98df-de2f44c694a6#breadcrumb\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Refero Styles\",\"item\":\"https://styles.refero.design\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Nornorm design system\",\"item\":\"https://styles.refero.design/style/0769ff4c-f719-4865-98df-de2f44c694a6\"}]},{\"@type\":\"CreativeWork\",\"@id\":\"https://styles.refero.design/style/0769ff4c-f719-4865-98df-de2f44c694a6#style-reference\",\"name\":\"Nornorm design system reference\",\"headline\":\"Nornorm design system | Refero Styles\",\"description\":\"Explore Nornorm's light Other design system: Canvas White #ffffff, Bone #f1efe9 colors, Lunar typography, and DESIGN.md for AI agents.\",\"url\":\"https://styles.refero.design/style/0769ff4c-f719-4865-98df-de2f44c694a6\",\"mainEntityOfPage\":\"https://styles.refero.design/style/0769ff4c-f719-4865-98df-de2f44c694a6\",\"isPartOf\":{\"@type\":\"WebSite\",\"name\":\"Refero Styles\",\"url\":\"https://styles.refero.design\"},\"isBasedOn\":{\"@type\":\"WebSite\",\"name\":\"Nornorm\",\"url\":\"https://nornorm.com\"},\"primaryImageOfPage\":{\"@type\":\"ImageObject\",\"@id\":\"https://styles.refero.design/style/0769ff4c-f719-4865-98df-de2f44c694a6#primaryimage\",\"url\":\"https://images.refero.design/styles/refero.design/image/fd6ff63e-07c1-4be7-b7b4-ee874381701f.jpg\",\"contentUrl\":\"https://images.refero.design/styles/refero.design/image/fd6ff63e-07c1-4be7-b7b4-ee874381701f.jpg\",\"caption\":\"Screenshot of Nornorm\"},\"image\":\"https://images.refero.design/styles/refero.design/image/fd6ff63e-07c1-4be7-b7b4-ee874381701f.jpg\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Refero Styles\",\"url\":\"https://styles.refero.design\"},\"publisher\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Refero\",\"url\":\"https://refero.design\"},\"keywords\":[\"Nornorm design system\",\"Nornorm website design\",\"Nornorm colors\",\"Nornorm typography\",\"DESIGN.md\",\"AI agent design\",\"website design inspiration\",\"Other design system\",\"Canvas White\",\"Bone\",\"Ash\",\"Stone\",\"Lunar\"],\"about\":[{\"@type\":\"Thing\",\"name\":\"Nornorm design system\"},{\"@type\":\"Thing\",\"name\":\"Nornorm website design\"},{\"@type\":\"Thing\",\"name\":\"Nornorm colors\"},{\"@type\":\"Thing\",\"name\":\"Nornorm typography\"},{\"@type\":\"Thing\",\"name\":\"DESIGN.md\"},{\"@type\":\"Thing\",\"name\":\"AI agent design\"},{\"@type\":\"Thing\",\"name\":\"website design inspiration\"},{\"@type\":\"Thing\",\"name\":\"Other design system\"}],\"datePublished\":\"2026-04-30T03:26:03.895Z\",\"dateModified\":\"2026-04-30T03:26:03.895Z\"}]}19:T4f0,**Quick Color Reference**\n- text: #000000 (primary) / #6a6a6a (secondary) / #ffffff (on dark or cobalt)\n- background: #ffffff (canvas) / #f1efe9 (bone section)\n- border: #000000 (structural) / #e5e5e5 (hairline on white controls)\n- accent: #1e37a0 Cobalt Ink (logo, active state, link emphasis only)\n- primary action: no distinct CTA color\n\n**Example Component Prompts**\nNo distinct primary action color was observed; use the extracted neutral button treatments instead of inventing a filled CTA color.\n2. Build a 4-column feature grid on a white #ffffff canvas. Each card: square image at top with 0px border-radius, then Lunar 20px weight 700 '01.' through '04.' in #000000, then heading at Lunar 20px weight 500 #000000, then body copy Lunar 16px weight 400 #6a6a6a. 24px gap between image and text, 32px column gap.\n3. Build a centered section header: Lunar 48px weight 400 #000000 heading with -1.44px letter-spacing, optional Lunar 20px weight 400 #6a6a6a subhead directly below with 8px gap. 64px bottom margin to the content. No decorative element.\n5. Build a client logo strip: white background, single row of 8 grayscale logos at uniform 24px height, evenly distributed across the full 1280px content width, 60% opacity to read as secondary social proof."
