.opencode/specs/sk-git/008-research-and-requirements/checklist.md:58:- [x] CHK-003 [P0] Lineage directories created under `research/lineages/` (`parallel-git-sol`, `parallel-git-luna`).
.opencode/specs/sk-git/008-research-and-requirements/checklist.md:68:- [x] CHK-011 [P0] Contradictions surfaced explicitly (SOL vs LUNA force-push, autostash, live-refs-vs-bundle). Evidence: `research/research.md` §2 divergence notes.
