 succeeded in 0ms:
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/013-create-skill-alignment/tasks.md:35:- [ ] T001 Pin the P3 minter, manifest-location, freshness, and runtime-discovery interfaces. (REQ-001, REQ-004; shared compiled-routing interface)
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/013-create-skill-alignment/implementation-summary.md:54:Implementation waits for the P3 minter, freshness predicate, canonical manifest location, and data-driven runtime discovery. After those interfaces stabilize, the two templates move together, the initializer gains the state adapter, and the existing create-skill contract suite expands to cover legacy, ready, and failure outcomes before any adoption claim.
