.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/014-benchmark-alignment/implementation-summary.md:45:| Verification | New Vitest suite and isolated fixtures | Prove fresh, divergent, drifted, missing, and broken states |
