.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/014-benchmark-alignment/plan.md:112:| Public compiled front door | Flag-gated served decision | Spawn with child-only env | Fresh, drifted, and broken fixtures |
