.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/010-live-activation/plan.md:212:3. Confirm `selectedPolicy` reverts to the prior generation and `servingAuthority` remains `legacy`.
