.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/011-runtime-engine/plan.md:165:- **Procedure**: Two independent reversals. Fleet-wide — unset `SPECKIT_COMPILED_ROUTING`, and the resolver returns null everywhere (legacy serves) with no manifest change. Per hub — `flip-serving.cjs --hub <id> --rollback` restores the byte-identical `manifest.serving-prior.json` and advances the fence; confirm `servingAuthority` reverts to `legacy` and `shadowOnly` to `true`. Retain the serving-prior for the full bake window before any cleanup.
